Pacific Gas and Electric Co said it willbuy back on July one 93.9 mln dlrs of two mortgage bond issues,Series 82A and 82B.    The redemption will save the company about 2.8 mln dlrs inannual financing costs for the remaining lives of the twomortgage bond issues, Pacific Gas said.    It will buy back the Series 82A bonds at 1,066.60 dlrs per1,000 dlr principal amount, plus one month's accrued interestof 12.81 dlrs. It will redeem the Series 82B at 1,105.20 dlrsper 1,000 dlr face amount, plus one month's accrued interest of11.14 dlrs. Reuter&#3;